title: Ep 52: Year In Review
description:
Today's proceedings:  We take a look back at each of our favorite stories of the year including a fiancé giving away a dog, a brother who feeds an egg to a cat, and a young fellow who didn't get invited to a party. We also learn our A-B-Sheesh with the Judgies and give out our year end superlatives!  

Thank you to every one for listening to the first year of the pod and we hope you stick around for the next one!
